---
title: Cheesy Chicken and Gnocchi with Garlic Green Peas
description: Tonight chicken teams up with supple gnocchi for a tasty Italian dinner the whole family will enjoy. A side of simple but elegant garlic green peas turns this into the perfect weeknight comfort food.
